caption:
I am so excited to have a special coming out on August 18th (Friday!) I started doing standup at 16 at the suggestion of my mom and in the 20 years since, it has brought me insane joy and also agony.
 
HELL was made under the bold leadership of @catsolen and @jenstatsky who made me feel like anything was possible, and without whom the special would just be 30 seconds and shot in my car.
 
I hope you like it, and I am so grateful for all of you. Without you, I would still be performing in venues that primarily do TNR meetups. Your support has given me a career when the industry said no wtf absolutely not. 
 
Thank you so much, Chris F.
